Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle with Akatsuki has finally begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidan's ability is revealed to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The team struggles in their fight against an amazingly powerful opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the situation growing desperate, Asuma tries to break through enemy lines, and his comrades can only watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Shikamaru backing him up, he managed to pull off an explosive combo attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hidan was engulfed in the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God has judged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what it means to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got my arm, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be one of his techniques or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the ceremony can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll suffer the unfathomable pain together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the ceremony can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll suffer the unfathomable pain together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Captain Asuma get burned, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't his fire technique hit the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it definitely hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some odd reason it hit Captain Asuma, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll make another 35 million ryou for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got everything set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, this's gonna hurt like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suck on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurts {\i1}good{\i0}, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nothin' like hitting an organ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that shit is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the other dies, his agony radiates through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And living through it is pure ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Asuma's holding his left leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's definitely wrong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy stabbed himself in the same leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're already under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's somehow managed to link our bodies together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if I attack him, I'll get hurt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...he can't be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do ya want it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout here? Or here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting it in both legs would be pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should I just end it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, don't use a physical attack like your Shadow Sewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the Shadow Neck Bind to keep him from moving! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo, how long has it been since you called for back-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only about ten minutes. It'll take at least another twenty for them to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kill him, we kill Captain Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Techniques like this usually remain in effect until the user releases them or gets killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every technique has some kind of risk, or restrictions on its use. There's gotta be a loophole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta calm down and analyze him carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru bought me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to use this opportunity to figure out how to undo this technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Shadow Neck Bind won't last long on an enemy of this caliber. I've only got a little time left to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's gonna take much longer, I'll kill them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting all that money get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to back the fuck off, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle these pussies on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're beyond lucky that this other guy hasn't attacked us, \Nespecially considering the situation we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, what on earth should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here prepared to fight enemies with abilities, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki had ten official members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Orochimaru abandoned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori of the Red Sands is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only three others that we know anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshigaki Kisame, who apparently took on Gai-sensei with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He uses water techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke's older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Sharingan user, Uchiha Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who in one second put Kakashi-san in the hospital for over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the guy Naruto fought, Deidara. He used explosive clay bombs that he controlled remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died trying to suicide-bomb them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fishy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're still five other members of Akatsuki. \NAnd not a single one listed in this file is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking time to study their techniques won't even scratch the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bet anything the remaining five have special abilities beyond my or anyone's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, these guys are ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to come up with a strategy beforehand is totally pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have to figure out how to handle them during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do I prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, I'll train and try to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do if I come across an opponent I just can't beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies' abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyze them, get the upper hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninjutsu, taijutsu, genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Determine which type the person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're two-man teams, it's possible they'll use combo attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider how their abilities complement one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll have to make judgments the moment I learn something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And against someone like Akatsuki, they probably won't give me time to figure anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you already trying to come up with strategies to use against Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I've just reached the conclusion that it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd come up with a strategy the second you got any information on them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming I get any information in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that'd be difficult if we went up against Akatsuki head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could kill me in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks, but these guys are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only if you were fighting an Akatsuki one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your abilities to analyze and make decisions under pressure are considered some of Konoha's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find time to do that in a one-on-one fight, then ask your friends for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a responsibility to your team, but if you're unable to rely on your teammates, then you're not fulfilling that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be times when you'd be toast on your own, but with your comrades' help, things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just saying things will work out isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And do it before your friends get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma's given me tons of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His speech, personality, tone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things he carries...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider everything he's done up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What those actions mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and how they're related to one-another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will tell me how and why his technique works, and the way to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God will smite assholes like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God...smite...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're already under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the ceremony can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse...ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got everything set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru's got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure something out, Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he think so clearly when he's gotta focus that hard on keeping his technique going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru can think ten steps ahead and consider 200 possible moves in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his real strength is his knack for choosing the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, Captain Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shadow technique forces the target to mimic the user's movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, he knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forcing him out of that weird symbol he drew on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get him out, then his technique, that curse, will be negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big scythe of his has three blades on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The design suggests it's meant to broaden the attack area rather than kill to deal a one-hit kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if it's a serious wound or a minor one, their only purpose is to draw blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, as long as he lands one attack, \Nhe can use that technique to kill his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are injuring the enemy and the curse related?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to form a link with the person he wants to curse, he has to ingest that person's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him lick off the blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just needs to open a wound, get a little blood on his scythe, and use it to curse his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body changed colors after he swallowed the blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one other condition for activating the curse, but it was pretty obvious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid's pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, he rushed over to that symbol he drew on the ground even though it meant running through Asuma's fire technique, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as soon as he was standing inside the diagram,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he said he was gonna start the ceremony and screamed about how everything was set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I determined that his curse technique was only ready once he entered the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He figured all that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I get free I'm gonna slash, bash and smash your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be an after for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Let's see if the curse has been lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can hold him much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Hurry the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me you thought your room was a bit bare?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino recommended these, hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be poppy seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the thought, but I'm sure I'd kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said they aren't too hard to manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, plant them if you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dumped them on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to plant them if I felt like it, but I can't just leave them like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Poppies...poppies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the language of flowers they mean "to comfort someone."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, talk about your close calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would've been completely wiped out if it hadn't been for Shikamaru's analytical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, he's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Asuma-san's so confident in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Now there's just one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you needed a hand, you should've asked me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you and your slow ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe before this all started you said, \N"Just shut the fuck up and watch, Kakuzu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, as a goddamned {\i1}head{\i0}, do you still think you can yell at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Okay, yes, I did tell you not to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I was trying to embarrass you or make you look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, man. C'mon and get my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, would you mind bringing my body over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.58,0:24:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu-chan, pretty please? With sugar on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! W-Wait! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, my body! Bring my body {\i1}here{\i0}, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.55,0:24:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head's lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.39,0:24:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.75,0:25:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow! You're ripping my hair out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.73,0:25:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to whine about pain, at least complain about your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.77,0:25:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dick! My neck isn't even in the same league!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.63,0:25:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some tiny little boo-boo, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even beheaded, he's still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.51,0:25:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fucking hurts like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cut my goddamned head off! This's like, hyper-mega-ultra pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.43,0:25:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... There's just no way to explain this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he's still alive, not in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without being attached to his body, he can't move or use any techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be immortal, but in that condition, he can't actually do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.66,0:25:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One down, one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.66,0:25:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.66,0:26:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's probably stronger and faster than that immortal bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.21,0:26:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also calm enough to not fight if he doesn't think he has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.12,0:26:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's so cruel and heartless that seeing his friend get his head chopped off didn't even faze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.71,0:26:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't discern his true power from that, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.62,0:26:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, he's so confident that I bet we haven't even seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.76,0:26:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the type of enemy that calculates the gap between his and his opponent's strength first.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.15,0:26:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the best thing we can do is demonstrate that we've got the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:26:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:26:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru's exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.86,0:27:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Captain Asuma's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.52,0:27:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gained the upper hand by disabling one of the Akatsuki, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it also means we've given ourselves a chance to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.43,0:27:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just worried about Shikamaru if we try...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.65,0:27:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give him an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.97,0:27:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.70,0:28:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've helped you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have to stay involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.13,0:28:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.81,0:28:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still, you baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.60,0:28:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.16,0:28:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.03,0:28:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.05,0:28:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got reattached!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.70,0:28:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All back together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.95,0:28:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the stitches, they'll break if you move too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, Kakuzu? Eat a dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.69,0:28:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are we fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.87,0:29:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've got a man who can't die and a man who can sew severed body parts back on like nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.24,0:29:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.74,0:29:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one thing after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.81,0:29:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They trump us no matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.72,0:29:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stupid ceremony is bad enough, but I'm sick of you dragging fights out with your blabbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.98,0:29:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.16,0:29:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm gonna get him for what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.42,0:29:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go breaking the commandments, now can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.79,0:29:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That again? Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.38,0:29:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.99,0:29:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.02,0:29:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.31,0:29:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suiton, Mizuame Nabara{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:57.33,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Suiton, Mizuame Nabara: Water Element, Syrup Snare Field)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.87,0:30:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.46,0:30:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.87,0:30:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume this was a combo where you force the enemy to focus on the flashy aerial attack, creating an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.25,0:30:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you attack from the ground with this strange liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.56,0:30:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So simplistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.94,0:30:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much wasted movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.44,0:30:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.42,0:30:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.43,0:30:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.22,0:31:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.49,0:31:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.79,0:31:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shi-!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.84,0:31:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting my time with your flailing...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.82,0:31:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, looks like Kakuzu's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.42,0:32:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get moving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.91,0:32:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise he'll bitch at me about my ritual taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.07,0:32:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.45,0:32:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.93,0:33:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.35,0:33:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get me with the same trick-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the same, you retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.75,0:34:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.34,0:34:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.16,0:34:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You said you wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.10,0:34:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sacrificing yourself to protect your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.85,0:34:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.69,0:34:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't this plan work?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.19,0:35:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my Shadow Sewing is successful, it'll bind one of the enemies and halve their fighting potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.42,0:35:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm going to connect from far away, we'll need to set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Sewing gets weaker the further I am from the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.81,0:35:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I use it at close range, the restraining power will increase, along with our chances for success!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.63,0:35:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this strategy does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.76,0:35:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A two-man lead placing you at the front next to me and my blades, so you can use Shadow Sewing as close as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.56,0:35:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, that'd give me the best chance of snaring the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.63,0:35:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru. I can't stress enough how highly I value your insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.91,0:35:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.10,0:35:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.86,0:35:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in this group is a superb ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.28,0:35:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a four-man cell comprised of three chuunin and a jounin,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.77,0:35:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a superior tactician in my squad that no one else has.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.77,0:36:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.04,0:36:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tactician bases his platoon's movements on the rear guard's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.09,0:36:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We rely on your judgment to make the right moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.83,0:36:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to make sure we're using our group's assets properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.83,0:36:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're out on the front line, it puts the mission's success at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.28,0:36:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.03,0:36:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how painful it is to lose a comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this's the best strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.67,0:36:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of the risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.23,0:36:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it means I can protect my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.94,0:36:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by comrades you mean this group, then you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we're protecting... The real reason we fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.70,0:37:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still don't understand, then there's no way I can put you out in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.16,0:37:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault! If...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.53,0:37:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd just thought of a better plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.58,0:37:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this wouldn't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.55,0:37:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you get it?! That's the best strategy we've got right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.47,0:37:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen Asuma get like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.27,0:37:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like sending in a single unit to break through enemy lines. \NSometimes, that's the only move you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You aren't cut out to be the Climbing Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't end up a sacrificial piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.52,0:37:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not with you behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.86,0:37:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.66,0:37:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.63,0:37:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.04,0:37:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't such a moron, this wouldn't have happened to Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.87,0:38:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it fucking hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.89,0:38:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.55,0:38:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to experience the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.41,0:38:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain that comes with killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.75,0:38:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.32,0:38:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.54,0:38:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.28,0:40:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.45,0:41:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.29,0:41:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.56,0:42:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother trying to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.80,0:42:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.72,0:42:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can already tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.35,0:42:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I finally understand why the Third did what he did to protect the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.64,0:43:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as always, I took too long to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.80,0:43:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino, Chouji, Shikamaru... I have one last thing to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.49,0:43:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Last Words.
